query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND mi.info in ('Swedish','Urdu','Bulgarian','Mongolian','Afrikaans','Rotuman','Chechen','Indonesian','Slovak') AND it1.info in ('book','production process protocol','taglines','height','LD video noise','languages','LD analog left','crazy credits','alternate versions','article','tech info','filming dates','bottom 10 rank','LD sharpness','LD group genre') AND mi_idx.info < '4.0' AND cct1.kind not in ('crew','cast','complete+verified') AND (k.keyword like '%suspense%' OR k.keyword like '%romance%' OR k.keyword like '%warrior%') AND t.title not like '%mirror%' AND t.title not like '%hat%' AND t.title not like '%microphone%' AND t.title not like '%time%' AND t.title not like '%road%' AND t.production_year < 2010 AND it2.info not in ('magazine cover photo','crazy credits','release dates','portrayed in','LD status of availablility','salary history') AND cct2.kind in ('crew','complete') AND n.name not like '%Z%' AND n.name not like '%b%' AND n.gender in ('m')
